c: 3
v: 11
t: "Koros Yallih farmoytiitit Abtah tan dirabboysiyyal firqawnaa kee firqawni maraay keenik duma Sugte korosuy Ni-Astooti dirabbosseh inna ken caagid, tokkel Yalli ken dambitteh Sabbatah ken yibbixeeh ken digaaleh, Yalli isil koroositeeh isi farmoytit dirabboyse maral gibdi digaala-li kinni"